Honolulu.KXRG-LP:
KXRG-LP, (95.9 FM), "My 95.9 FM", is a non-commercial FM Dance Top 40 outlet serving the Honolulu, Hawaii area. The station is owned by Ohana Broadcasters Corporation and is licensed to Honolulu.


== Station history ==
From March 2006 to July 2007, KXRG-LP was on 101.1 MHz as "Energy 101.1".
